        "Question": "The following are excluded from the coverage of Title I, Book II of Labor Code of the Philippines (Conditions of Employment) except: (2012 Bar Question) a) Field personnel; b) Supervisors; c) Managers; d) Employees of government-owned and controlled corporations.",
        "Answer": "(b) Supervisors [Art. 82, Labor Code]"
