        "Answer": "FALSE. Seafarers as overseas Filipino workers are fixed-term employees whose continued rehiring should not be interpreted as a basis for regularization but rather as a series of contract renewals sanctioned under the doctrine set by Millares vs. NLRC (Gu-Miro v. Adorable, 437 SCRA 162 )."
