        "Answer": "(A) Constant and Able should be held solidarily liable for the unpaid wages and benefits, as well as backwages and separation pay, based on Article 109 of the Labor Code which provides that every employer or indirect employer shall be held responsible with his contractor or subcontractor for any violation of any provision of this Code."
