        "Answer": "No. In their employer-employee relationship, Don Jose and Mang Kiko are not compulsory covered by the Social Security System because Mang Kiko is rendering domestic services in a private home which is one of the kinds of employment excluded from the compulsory coverage of the Social Security System."
